Create Shell, and navigation mechanism.

* Add icons

* Add clickable URL

* Add new icon for generator in menu

* Add version to menu

* Add IOS version

* Update README.md

* Add template Uwp project

* Improved App Start up

* Add assets, and ensure menuitem is highlighted

* Improve the trash icon

* Test on Win10 Phone

* Adding new image assets for UWP store etc, more to come

* Decrease version font.
Add some artifact files from UWP to ignore list

* New Windows Store assets

* New Android screenshots

* Increment Android version

* Updated Tablet screenshot
